#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:1
msgid "Disaggregated Diffusion Pipeline"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:3
msgid ""
"Split a monolithic text-to-video/image pipeline into independent "
"**Encoder**, **Denoiser**, and **Decoder** roles, each running on its own "
"GPU(s). A central **DiffusionServer** routes requests through the pipeline."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:5
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:7
msgid ""
"Disaggregation is controlled by a single flag: `--disagg-role`. Each "
"component is launched independently, just like LLM PD disaggregation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "`--disagg-role`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "What it runs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "`monolithic`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "(Default) Standard single-server mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "`encoder`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid ""
"All stages with the default `RoleType.ENCODER` affinity: "
"`InputValidationStage`, `TextEncodingStage` (plus `ImageEncodingStage` / "
"`ImageVAEEncodingStage` for image-conditioned pipelines), "
"`LatentPreparationStage`, `TimestepPreparationStage`, and any model-specific "
"\"before denoising\" stage (e.g. `QwenImageLayeredBeforeDenoisingStage`, "
"`GlmImageBeforeDenoisingStage`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "`denoiser`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid ""
"`DenoisingStage` (and its subclasses: `CausalDMDDenoisingStage`, "
"`DmdDenoisingStage`, `LTX2AVDenoisingStage`, `LTX2RefinementStage`, "
"`Hunyuan3DShapeDenoisingStage`, ...) — the DiT forward loop plus the "
"scheduler stepping it drives."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "`decoder`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid ""
"`DecodingStage` (VAE decode) and its subclasses (`LTX2AVDecodingStage`, "
"`HeliosDecodingStage`, ...)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "`server`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:0
msgid "DiffusionServer head node + HTTP server (no GPU)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:17
msgid ""
"Each stage declares its role via the `role_affinity` property on "
"`PipelineStage` (default `ENCODER`). When `--disagg-role` is not "
"`monolithic`, the pipeline only instantiates stages whose affinity matches, "
"so the above table is the source of truth for what actually runs in each "
"process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:19
msgid "Single-Machine Example (Verified)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:21
msgid ""
"The following commands have been tested end-to-end on an 8×H200 machine with "
"`Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers`. Each role runs on a separate GPU via `--"
"base-gpu-id`; the `server` head node requires no GPU."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:25
msgid ""
"# Terminal 1: Encoder (GPU 0)\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role encoder \\\n"
"    --disagg-server-addr tcp://127.0.0.1:19655 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19000 \\\n"
"    --num-gpus 1 --base-gpu-id 0\n"
"\n"
"# Terminal 2: Denoiser (GPU 1)\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role denoiser \\\n"
"    --disagg-server-addr tcp://127.0.0.1:19655 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19001 \\\n"
"    --num-gpus 1 --base-gpu-id 1\n"
"\n"
"# Terminal 3: Decoder (GPU 2)\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role decoder \\\n"
"    --disagg-server-addr tcp://127.0.0.1:19655 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19002 \\\n"
"    --num-gpus 1 --base-gpu-id 2\n"
"\n"
"# Terminal 4: DiffusionServer head (no GPU, receives HTTP requests)\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role server \\\n"
"    --encoder-urls  \"tcp://127.0.0.1:19000\" \\\n"
"    --denoiser-urls \"tcp://127.0.0.1:19001\" \\\n"
"    --decoder-urls  \"tcp://127.0.0.1:19002\" \\\n"
"    --host 0.0.0.0 --port 22000 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19655\n"
"\n"
"# Send request (video generation)\n"
"curl http://127.0.0.1:22000/v1/videos \\\n"
"    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n"
"    -d '{\"model\": \"Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B-Diffusers\", \"prompt\": \"A "
"curious raccoon exploring a garden, cinematic\", \"size\": \"832x480\"}'\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:62
msgid ""
"**Tested result (8×H200):** Encoder 2.3 s (TextEncoding) → Denoiser 312.8 s "
"(50 steps, layerwise offload) → Decoder 7.1 s (VAE decode). Total ~322 s for "
"81-frame 1024×1024 video."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:66
msgid ""
"**Tip:** `--base-gpu-id` controls which physical GPU the role uses. Encoder "
"and Decoder can share a GPU (e.g. both `--base-gpu-id 0`) to save resources, "
"but make sure the combined GPU memory is sufficient."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:70
msgid "Multi-Machine Example"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:72
msgid ""
"The exact same CLI pattern — just replace `127.0.0.1` with actual IPs and "
"add RDMA flags for direct transfer:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/disaggregation.md:75
msgid ""
"# Machine A (10.0.0.1): Encoder\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-14B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role encoder \\\n"
"    --disagg-server-addr tcp://10.0.0.4:19655 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19000 \\\n"
"    --num-gpus 1 \\\n"
"    --disagg-p2p-hostname 10.0.0.1 --disagg-ib-device mlx5_0\n"
"\n"
"# Machine B (10.0.0.2): Denoiser (4 GPUs with SP)\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-14B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role denoiser \\\n"
"    --disagg-server-addr tcp://10.0.0.4:19655 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19001 \\\n"
"    --num-gpus 4 --denoiser-sp 4 --denoiser-ulysses 2 --denoiser-ring 2 \\\n"
"    --disagg-p2p-hostname 10.0.0.2 --disagg-ib-device mlx5_0\n"
"\n"
"# Machine C (10.0.0.3): Decoder\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-14B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role decoder \\\n"
"    --disagg-server-addr tcp://10.0.0.4:19655 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19002 \\\n"
"    --num-gpus 1 \\\n"
"    --disagg-p2p-hostname 10.0.0.3 --disagg-ib-device mlx5_0\n"
"\n"
"# Machine D (10.0.0.4): DiffusionServer head\n"
"sglang serve --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-14B-Diffusers \\\n"
"    --disagg-role server \\\n"
"    --encoder-urls  \"tcp://10.0.0.1:19000\" \\\n"
"    --denoiser-urls \"tcp://10.0.0.2:19001\" \\\n"
"    --decoder-urls  \"tcp://10.0.0.3:19002\" \\\n"
"    --host 0.0.0.0 --port 30000 \\\n"
"    --scheduler-port 19655 \\\n"
"    --disagg-dispatch-policy max_free_slots\n"
msgstr ""

